Package: rsei
Type: Package
Title: Seamless Integration with the 'Sistema Eletrônico de Informações (SEI)' <https://is.gd/n5CNEj>
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-01-02
Authors@R: c(
  person("Andre", "Leite", email = "leite@castlab.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Hugo", "Vaconcelos", email = "hugo.vasconcelos@ufpe.br", role = "aut"),
  person("Diogo", "Bezerra", email = "diogo.bezerra@ufpe.br", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides an 'R'-based toolkit for interacting with the 'Sistema Eletrônico de Informações (SEI)' <https://is.gd/n5CNEj>, the official electronic system for document and process management used by Brazil's Federal Public Administration. This package offers end-to-end support for 'SOAP' communication with 'SEI', allowing users to create, retrieve, and manage processes and documents. Core features include utilities to build 'SOAP' envelopes, parse 'XML' responses, handle multi-part file uploads, and securely store credentials. Streamline your 'SEI' workflows with a consistent and user-friendly 'R' interface.
